{"tid":937400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有咁嘅諗法係咪應該落地獄","createTime":"2018-12-11T13:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T08:58:25.000Z","uid":130406,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"674b6f7750b067fa50a5fca8d6ef16ef5c0ae0f5","tid":937400,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"今日搭車 巴士滿唒座<br />\n我早上車就揾到位坐 <br />\n之後我隔離有個大嚿黑人手攞住好多嘢無得坐要企<br />\n心入面覺得好正好有優越感 偷偷地笑咗幾聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得就好似返到殖民時代咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班低等Nigger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係唔準坐<br />\n最好第時分開一個無凳車箱畀黑人同南亞狗咪畀佢地同我地同一卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e79eff3c11423c6d9cb941348f1b5249ab24ce","tid":937400,"uid":204717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:42:18.000Z","msg":"第時係你要企班蝻亞同黑人坐啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望下街上面班蝻同你架數量升得幾快先得架<br />\n香港人又唔生 大陸人都愈生愈少<br />\n睇下歐洲蛔化就知咩事"},{"pid":"10ea36a4cff515c71f273d8923d89ce4bf853716","tid":937400,"uid":17184,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"車<span style=\"color: red;\">廂</span>"},{"pid":"44b36c7e0092022a6bd6cedf91287a2c5db37c69","tid":937400,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}